+## iMessage privacy and operations
+
+Run `imsg chats --limit 100 --json` on macOS to choose approved numeric chat
+IDs, then configure `enabled`, `chatIds`, optional advanced `participants`,
+`windowHours`, and `maxMessagesPerChat`. Run
+`openwiki ingest imessage --print`; set `OPENWIKI_WIKI_DIR` to an absolute path
+when synthesized pages belong in another wiki or vault.
