+permissions are unnecessary. The all-source schedule uses launchd label
+`com.openwiki.ingestion`; inspect the first `ProgramArguments` executable in
+`~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.openwiki.ingestion.plist`, grant that executable
+Full Disk Access if needed, and verify with:
